org.jmisb.api.klv.st0903.shared

Class LocationPack

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jmisb.api.klv.st0903.shared.LocationPack

  • public class LocationPack
extends Object
    Location Pack.

    This data transfer object supports various Boundary Series and Target Location.

    Latitude, longitude and HAE are always required.

    If setting individual components, be aware that the standard deviations are conceptually a single group. Similarly, the correlation values are "grouped". Unless all the elements in a group are set, it won't make sense. Further, if the correlation group values are set, the standard deviation group values also need to be set.
